Africa, the News Agency of Nigeria reported today.
</P>
<P>
In a communique signed in Abuja on Sunday at the end of his
two-day official visit to Nigeria, Gambian President Yaya Jamen
and his host, General Sani Abacha re-affirmed their commitment to
peace and security in their respective countries.
