rocked by wars and refugee problems, and reiterated the need to
safeguard the sovereignty and independence of Zaire.
</P>
<P>
The two leaders stressed the need to refer all issues of
conflict in the continent to existing OAU mechanisms for peaceful
resolution of conflicts rather than resort to violence.
</P>
