<HEADLINE> Mkapa Commends Japan for Supporting Tanzania </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, March 3 (Xinhua) -- Tanzanian President
Benjamin Mkapa today commended the Japanese government for having
all along positively supported his country's efforts towards
self-reliance since independence.
</P>
<P>
In a discussion with visiting special assistant to the
