<HEADLINE> East China Province Taking Early Anti-Flood Precautions </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANGZHOU, March 4 (Xinhua) -- At the of beginning of this year,
authorities in east China's Zhejiang Province started taking
preventative measures against possible flooding.
</P>
<P>
Various exercises and meetings have been held by the provincial
departments in charge since January to ensure the safety of life
around local rivers, lakes, and reservoirs.
</P>
<P>
