<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, March 4 (Xinhua) -- Non-governmental humanitarian
organizations in Ethiopia were encouraged to focus on development
activities rather than humanitarian work, officials from the
Disaster Prevention and Preparedness Commission of Ethiopia said
here today.
</P>
<P>
