<HEADLINE> Jiang Stresses Adherence to Party's Basic Line  (6) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jiang pointed out that this year will be a crucial one for the
the history of the country's development, when the Chinese
government will resume the exercise of its sovereignty over Hong
Kong and the Party will convene its 15th National Congress.
</P>
<P>
The first event will be of important and far-reaching
significance to the accomplishment of China's reunification cause
and boost the national morale, he said.
</P>
<P>
And the 15th National Party Congress will be an historic event,
which will unite and lead the entire Chinese people in advancing
in an all-round way the great cause of building socialism with
Chinese characteristics into the next century, Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
"Both events will be focuses of world attention," he said.
</P>
