Bureau of the CPC Central Committee and vice-chairman of the
Central Military Commission, presided over the meeting, which was
also attended by Zhang Zhen, Zhang Wan'nian and Chi Haotian, all
vice-chairmen of the CMC, and Fu Quanyou and Yu Yongbo, members of
