<HEADLINE> Jiang Stresses Adherence to Party's Basic Line (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"In carrying forward at the behest of Comrade Deng Xiaoping and
living up to his long-cherished wishes, we must get down to
actions and concentrate all our mind and energy on the Party's
cause as well as army building," Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
By now, China has mapped out a trans-century blueprint for its
reform and construction and major principles and policies in
different fields of work in army building has been ascertained, he
said.
</P>
<P>
"Whether these goals can be carried out and the principles and
policies be implemented hinges largely on the political quality
and ideological state of the senior army officers as well as well
their style of work and practice," he said.
</P>
<P>
Jiang urged the army officers to be aware of the arduous task,
tremendous responsibility and the need to set high criteria and
strict requirements in study, work and ideological work. Army
officers must also have it in mind to maintain close ties with the
masses and serve the people heart and soul.
</P>
<P>
All theories and practices of Deng Xiaoping, he said, are
centered on one basic purpose, and that is to work for the
interests of the people. And Deng's starting point in considering
all issues is precisely to see whether the people are happy,
contented and agree or not, he said.
</P>
<P>
The letter to the Party Central Committee by Comrade Deng
Xiaoping's family members eloquently shows the noble character and
sterling integrity. "What is a thorough materialist, what is meant
by giving his all till his heart stops beating, and what can be
called selfless sacrifice? --- Comrade Deng Xiaoping has provided
the most convincing answer with his own brilliant life," he said.
</P>
<P>
"We should not only study Deng's thinking and theories, but
earnestly learn from his revolutionary spirit and noble ideals,"
he said.
</P>
<P>
He called on all comrades to, following Deng Xiaoping's
example, foster correct world outlook, and the outlook on life and
values, and seek no fame, status and promotion, give priority to
the Party and people's interests, so as to perform feats in
revolutionizing and modernizing the army and make it a still more
regular armed force.
</P>
