<HEADLINE> Jiang Stresses Adherence to Party's Basic Line (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jiang pointed out that officers and soldiers of the whole army
should be organized to study Deng Xiaoping's theory of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics, and be armed with this
scientific theory.
</P>
<P>
"This is a strategic task that must be unremittingly stressed
and carried out in a down-to-earth manner for a long period of
time," he said, adding that the fond memories of the late Comrade
Deng Xiaoping should be turned into a powerful impetus to study,
research, publicize and apply Deng's scientific theory.
</P>
<P>
"We must make painstaking efforts in study and research to
acquire a profound understanding of the fundamental tenets and
ideological essence of this theory, try hard to learn and grasp
Comrade Xiaoping's stand, viewpoints, and methods for observing,
analyzing and solving problems, and continuously enhance our
conscientiousness and firmness in adhering to the Party's basic
line," he said.
</P>
<P>
He said that it is very important for the military to fully
understand Deng Xiaoping's thinking on army building in the new
historical period, which is a major integral part of the theory of
building socialism with Chinese characteristics, and a scientific
guideline for the building of the PLA under new historical
conditions.
</P>
<P>
"We should persistently take Deng Xiaoping's thinking on army
building in the new historical period as the guideline, and
actively explore characteristics and laws of army building at a
time when profound changes have taken place in the global
strategic structure, in a social environment of developing a
socialist market economy and opening to the outside world, and
against a background of significant changes in the military field
worldwide caused by a rapid progress of science and technology,"
he said.
</P>
<P>
He called on the army to make every effort to strengthen itself
comprehensively, acquire the ability to win local wars fought with
modern technologies, especially with high technologies, and
improve its combat effectiveness, so as to fulfill all tasks given
by the Party and the people.
</P>
<P>
He stressed that senior officers must take a leading role in
studying and applying the Party's basic theories and line to live
up to the trust and expectations of the Party and the people.
</P>
<P>
"Comrade Xiaoping always placed great hopes on senior officers
of the army. Now that the historical responsibility of army
building has fallen onto our shoulders, it is up to us to preserve
the nature of the people's army, forever ensure its loyalty to the
Party, the country, the people and socialism, and accomplish our
mission in accordance with Comrade Xiaoping's wishes," he said.
</P>
</TEXT>
