<HEADLINE> Jiang Stresses Adherence to Party's Basic Line (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 4 (Xinhua) -- To modernize China and revitalize
the Chinese nation, the most important and fundamental thing to do
is to hold high the banner of Deng Xiaoping's theory of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics and firmly adhere to the
Party's basic line, President Jiang Zemin said here today.
</P>
<P>
"On this vital political issue that concerns the future
and destiny of the Party, the state and the nation, there must not
be the slightest ambiguity or vacillation," he said.
</P>
<P>
Jiang, who is also the General Secretary of the Central
Committee of the Communist Party of China (CPC) and Chairman of
the Central Military Commission, made the remark at a meeting
attended by all deputies to the National People's Congress
(NPC) from the People's Liberation Army.
</P>
<P>
The deputies are here attending the ongoing session of the
Eighth NPC.
</P>
<P>
The great achievements China has made in its economy and social
development since the Third Plenary Meeting of the 11th CPC
Central Committee in 1978, the quick recovery and revitalization
of its socialist cause from the catastrophe caused by the
decade-long Cultural Revolution, and China's invincible position
in a turbulent international arena, all these, in the final
analysis, have been due to the fact that China has Deng Xiaoping's
theory of building socialism with Chinese characteristics and that
the CPC has a basic line that has taken shape under the direction
of this theory, he said.
</P>
<P>
The overall situation in China is good, Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
"We will face some new trials on the road of progress, which
requires that we keep a clear head. We should firmly persist in
taking economic development as our central task and unify, in a
dialectical way, the Four Cardinal Principles and reform and
opening-up, to ensure that our modernization drive always progress
successfully on a correct path."
</P>
<P>
He urged the PLA, as an armed force to carry out revolutionary
political tasks, to keep firmly in mind Deng Xiaoping's
entrustment, carry out the Party's line and policies in an
exemplary way, and make greater contributions to safeguarding
national security and promoting national development.
</P>
</TEXT>
