<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, March 4 (Xinhua) -- Three people were shot dead and
another was injured today by rebels of the Liberation Tigers of
Tamil Elam (LTTE) in the Northern Central Province of Sri Lanka,
according to police sources here.
